QuestData.Title: The Demons Below
QuestData.Description: Something, someone, intended us to never awaken. I sense their presence is still here in the barrow.$B$B<Koda takes a moment to stand.>$B$BMy body is weak from deep slumber.$B$BIf you would aid us, clear our barrow of any enemies.
QuestData.CompletionText: This was no accident. Someone intended us to sleep forever.
QuestData.RewardText: Excellent. The chambers are clear. Very impressive, $c.
